description: This is a historic land, associated with the Vedas. There was also a salt Satyagraha here led by Rajaji & local fishermen: PM @narendramodi — narendramodi_in (@narendramodi_in) May 11,

message:
At Vedaranyam rally, highlighted why TN needs a change from the 2 parties that are ruling in the state for years. Shared details about how the Sagarmala project will transform lives of people in coastal areas & benefits of MUDRA Yojana for youth of TN.

TN can’t afford a corrupt Govt. When previous Govt. was in power at the Centre there were many scams. Corruption adversely impacts progress.  http://nm-4.com/feuo
